2 May 2013Members of the media are invited to the briefing by the Justice, Crime Prevention and Security Cluster Ministers to update on the Indian delegation that landed at the Waterkloof Air Force Base. The details are as follows: Date: Friday, 03 May 2013 Time: 10h00 Venue: GCIS Auditorium, 1st Floor, Midtown Building, cnr Sisulu and Madiba Sts, Pretoria NB: There will be a video-link to Imbizo Media Centre, 120 Plein Street, Parliament, Cape TownKindly confirm attendance by e-mail or sms to: Tshegofatso Modubu (Pretoria) E-mail: tshegofatso@gcis.gov.za Cell: 083 276 0786 Liezil Cerf (Cape Town) E-mail: liezil@gcis.gov.za Cell: 076 778 2380 Enquiries: Phumla Williams Cell: 083 501 0139